# Compliance Rule

## Invariants (never violate)
- INV-001: Every dossier claim has `[Source: KEY]` in evidence ledger
- INV-002: Guardrail strips uncited/invalid claims — never bypass
- INV-004: Audit logs append-only with hashed payloads
- INV-007: HITL cases require `POST /cases/:id/approve`

## Key files
- Guardrail: `src/graph/nodes/guardrail.ts`
- Reports: `src/services/reports/generator.ts`
- Audit: `src/services/audit/logger.ts`
- Evidence schema: `src/db/schema.ts` → `evidence` table

## ADRs
- ADR-002: HITL as API pause
- ADR-005: Evidence hash chain
- ADR-007: Zod for all LLM outputs

## On review
Adopt COMPLIANCE_OFFICER role. Fill all invariant checks in SESSION_STATE.
